Mildred Joanne Smith https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mildred_Joanne_Smith 0 Mildred Joanne Smith (May 16, 1921 – July 19, 2015) was an American actress, singer, magazine editor and teacher. In her brief acting career, she performed in a number of Broadway shows and in only one film, No Way Out, alongside Sidney Poitier.
